data.meta_description:
255 likes, 4 comments - royals_and_nobility on November 15, 2021: "Bulgarian #royals
🔸️HRH Prince Boris, Prince of Tarnovo, Duke in Saxony, Prince of Saxe Coburg & Gotha
🔹️ known by his Spanish civilian name Boris de Sajonia-Coburgo-Gotha y Ungría, is the elder son of Miriam Ungría y López and Kardam, Prince of Turnovo, and the grandson of former Tsar Simeon II of Bulgaria.
🔹️He is, after the death of his father on 7 April 2015, first in line of succession to the Bulgarian throne.
🔹️Boris, who has maintained close relations with the Spanish royal family since his father's death. 
🔹️He speaks Spanish, English, French & Bulgarian.
🔹️ He is an artist, devoted to sculpture, plays the guitar
🔹️He will rule under the name of "Tsar Boris IV" if the monarchy is restored in Bulgaria during his time

#royalfamily #royalfamilies #bulgaria #germanroyals #bulgarianroyalfamily #royalsandnobility #nobility #royalstyle".
